      "comment": "BACKROWER (1) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 10 lengths (20.42) at this track in a Maiden over 352m. Leading chance again. LAKODA MILEY (7) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. GOLDEN SPARKLES (2) is a handily bred pup making her debut without a trial. Can measure up. HARD STYLE MISS (3) is new to this circuit but can play a major role.",
